              sem. Nulla consequat massa quis enim.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class={styles.pic}>
          <Image src="../img/img1.png" alt="" width="600px" height="350px" />
        </div>
      </div>

        <div class={styles.keyword}>
          <div class={styles.subheading}>
            <h2>Type your text or paste here(ctrl+v) </h2>
